==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sorbonist
<hw>Sor"bon*ist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>sorboniste</ets>.]</ety> <def>A doctor of the <xex>Sorbonne</xex>,
or theological college, in the University of Paris, founded by Robert de
<xex>Sorbon</xex>, <sc>a. d.</sc> 1252. It was suppressed in the
Revolution of 1789.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sorcerer</ent>⟦br⟧
